{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"54708-guliyo-sya-u","title":"गुलियो स्याउ","description":"रजनी आफ्नै ढङ्‌गले चित्र बनाउँछिन्‌ । रजनीकी आमा भने फरक चित्र हुनुपर्ने कुरा गर्छिन्‌ । आखिरमा रजनी आमालाई कसरी चित्त बुभाउँछिन्‌ त ?","language":"Nepali","langCode":"ne","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kedar  Shrestha"],"illustrators":["Binita  Buddhacharya"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/54708-guliyo-sya-u"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/103153/size3/45642f52073d8a93beb638ee9b9ded79.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/103153/size6/45642f52073d8a93beb638ee9b9ded79.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/97078/size6/369b05c5f4176e725550090e3956d401.jpg","text":"रजनी चित्र–किताबमा रङ लगाउन थालिन् ।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/97079/size6/0ee68b734a3be2a0f3c05457ec790485.jpg","text":"घाम त पहेँलो हुन्छ, होइन र छोरी? \nयो त बिहानको घाम हो नि आमा !","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/97080/size6/361ef2a535c6898f55a04c6467250fc8.jpg","text":"रजनीले पातमा खैरो रङ लगाइन् । \nपात त हरियो हुन्छ होइन र छोरी ?","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/97081/size6/fa27c409082ca3362eda24b0d62cd256.jpg","text":"सुकेको पात त खैरो नै हुन्छ नि, आमा !","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/97082/size6/a64eee9ef3a6ff33a230aa142a411daa.jpg","text":"आमा, यीः कति राम्रो फूल ! \nहाम्रो गमलाको फूल त रातो छ नि, छोरी \n! \nतर स्कुलको गमलामा त पहेँलो फूल छ नि आमा!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/97083/size6/9e0cbadc2bbc459d725c891115a92f8f.jpg","text":"लौ, आकाश नीलो हुनुपर्ने होइन र छोरी ? \nरातको आकाश त कालो देखिन्छ नि आमा !","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/97084/size6/aaa77fe409c0eea02de88363bd5d063f.jpg","text":"स्याउ त रातो हुनुपर्ने होइन र ? यो नपाकेको स्याउ, क्या आमा ! \nधेरैजसो हरियो स्याउ त अमिलो हुन्छ नि छोरी\n।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/97085/size6/a335360ddf5740b12af902e39632f11d.jpg","text":"किन पीर मान्नुहुन्छ आमा ! लिनुस्, तपाईंलाई चाहिँ गुलियो स्याउ ।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":117}}